title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1990-06-15
taper: Rick Katzeff and Dave Brotman and Ted Mattes and Marco Fanari
description:
Set 1

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower, Minglewood Blues, A Little Light, Stagger Lee, Desolation Row, Ramble On Rose, Hell In A Bucket

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Blow Away, Women Are Smarter-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Around & Around, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door
